  "description": "AMPULLAE at 0.0 — zero sensitivity. The stoic hammerhead. Velocity, aftertouch, expression change nothing. The sound is what it is regardless of how you touch it. VA triangle (Voice 1) and KS pluck (Voice 2) in LOVE at +0.6. The voices fuse into a hybrid that is neither analog nor physical — a new timbre that exists only through their blend. The stoic receives without reacting. Designed for layering under more expressive instruments where you need a stable foundation that will not shift.",
